    <summary>Templates for the three-tier context pyramid: CLAUDE.md hook, AGENTS.md 20-80 line brief, and .agents/INDEX.md deep references. One source of truth serving Claude Code and standalone agents.</summary>
    <category>kb</category>
    <difficulty>beginner</difficulty>
    <created>2026-04-29</created>
    <tags>
      <tag>documentation</tag>
      <tag>agents-md</tag>
